{"tid":1386050,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"打機一定要識組隊！","createTime":"2019-07-30T08:43:59.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-30T08:54:54.000Z","uid":102983,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"4a5920c82f0851ee0f2171e341fdd04c5610f401","tid":1386050,"uid":102983,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T08:43:59.000Z","msg":"之前打機<br />\n行軍打仗 人一多就行得慢 又要糧食 裝備又貴 硬碰硬人地裝備一勁過我 我就輸 根本贏唔到<br />\n之後我醒左 搵啲精銳部隊玩突襲<br />\n人一少 就指揮得快 配合又好 機動性又高<br />\n分大隊細隊<br />\n大隊可能30人 大隊長諗戰略 諗目的<br />\n細分5人一小隊 小隊長諗戰術 點行動 點配合<br />\n6隊人一齊行動 行動完就走 一隊有危險 其他隊去救 救完即走<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">最緊要係我行動無其他人知 如果有敵方間諜 就會全軍覆沒</span></span><br />\n<br />\n次次用依招都以少勝多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9c8bbddc9a747ca6c053b09af317bb8e93c9755c","tid":1386050,"uid":1392,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T08:44:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n夢想做工程師或者汽車維修員既同學仔入一入黎<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1383220\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1383220</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />幫手推"},{"pid":"efceff119fef4ce8cd6593e60461b6eefdb6fcb5","tid":1386050,"uid":102983,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T08:54:54.000Z","msg":"無人打機？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}